data.description: Welcome to this four-bedroom three bath home nestled in the city of Moreno Valley. Upon entering the property, you will be greeted by the spacious family room featuring carpet flooring, high ceilings, and immediate access to the dining area and living room. The dining area is very spacious and has beautiful hardwood flooring. This property has an open floorplan that you can immediately head onto your living room that features hardwood flooring, great natural light, and a fireplace. The kitchen has a spacious island, recessed lighting, plenty of cabinetry, and immediate access to your laundry room and backyard.  Head on over to the master bedroom with a full master bathroom, a spacious walk-in closet, and enough space for a king-size bed. The master Bathroom has dual sinks, hardwood flooring, and a bathtub separate from your shower. The three bedrooms of this home are all ample in size and have great closet space. Outback Lounge in the private and serene backyard that features spaces to put your outdoor furniture to entertain your guests, plenty of space for gardening and outdoor activities, a covered patio, and your own fountain, not to mention a private gate for RV Parking. This home also comes with a 3-car garage perfect for storage or for a family with many cars and an ample driveway with its own space for RV Parking. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home in a wonderful, established neighborhood in Moreno Valley close to schools, shopping centers, and freeways.
